About this hotel

This sprawling high-end hotel is 5 km from Royal Golf Marrakech, 6 km from the Bahia Palace with 160 rooms, and 8 km from the 12th-century Koutoubia Mosque.

Check-in time: 3:00 PM
Check-out time: 12:00 PM

    I booked the Suite Deluxe with the view on the pool as a birthday surprise for my best friend, and the staff was beyond helpful and accommodating to make the surprise and the stay the most perfect.

    The room is beautifully made and furnished, and is quite large and bright; we loved its home-y cosy but still refined design. Extra love for the mattresses that were extremely comfortable : I slept like a baby !!

Another shoutout for the wonderful cuisine : the dinner was a pleasure to our tastebuds and we loved and enjoyed every moment of it. The breakfast was filling, tasty and diversified and the service impeccable.

    Annakhil

    The sprawling suburb of Annakhil includes golf courses and palm groves, with paths and horse-carriage tours through 100,000 trees at El Palmeral. Inside that park is Muse de la Palmeraie, showing a century of Moroccan paintings in a 1940s colonial farmhouse. MACAAL is a more modern space, displaying pan-African art. Residential areas have casual tagine restaurants, while resort hotels have chic bars and bistros.

    About this hotel

    This sprawling high-end hotel is 5 km from Royal Golf Marrakech, 6 km from the Bahia Palace with 160 rooms, and 8 km from the 12th-century Koutoubia Mosque.

    Offering terraces and private gardens, the refined, warmly furnished suites have free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs, fireplaces, and living areas with sofas. Upgraded suites add massage facilities, and there are 2-bedroom villas.

    Freebies include parking, and breakfast which is served in an elegant restaurant. There's a relaxed lobby bar and an eatery by an outdoor pool, as well as a gym and tennis courts. The luxe spa offers steam baths, massages and aromatherapy treatments.
